WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.449 --> 00:00:04.940
Coral Princess is home to 16 decks of

00:00:04.940 --> 00:00:08.559
intimate venues and tasteful amenities.

00:00:08.559 --> 00:00:11.660
You'll notice their style and grace the

00:00:11.660 --> 00:00:13.490
moment you enter the stunning four-story

00:00:13.490 --> 00:00:16.100
atrium lobby. Sample the wide array of

00:00:16.100 --> 00:00:18.050
specialties at the International Café.

00:00:18.050 --> 00:00:20.510
And peruse a selection of duty-free

00:00:20.510 --> 00:00:24.980
shopping choices. On Promenade Deck, Enjoy

00:00:24.980 --> 00:00:28.600
a cigar in the dapper Churchill Lounge.

00:00:28.600 --> 00:00:31.700
Or explore the outer decks and discover

00:00:31.700 --> 00:00:35.210
delightful freshwater pools. Nestled near

00:00:35.210 --> 00:00:37.870
the bow is an inviting splash pool.

00:00:37.870 --> 00:00:40.480
Midship is the sparkling Lido pool,

00:00:40.480 --> 00:00:43.130
featuring our spectacular Movies Under

00:00:43.130 --> 00:00:45.440
the Stars outdoor theater experience. And

00:00:45.440 --> 00:00:48.500
the tranquil Lotus pool with retractable

00:00:48.500 --> 00:00:52.399
roof. Center Court, up on the aft Sports

00:00:52.399 --> 00:00:54.140
Deck, will keep you active with

00:00:54.140 --> 00:00:57.770
pickleball. basketball and more. The

00:00:57.770 --> 00:01:00.079
Sanctuary is a quiet, on-deck retreat,

00:01:00.079 --> 00:01:02.600
exclusively for adults and attended by

00:01:02.600 --> 00:01:04.729
Serenity Stewards for the ultimate in

00:01:04.729 --> 00:01:07.710
pampered relaxation.

00:01:07.710 --> 00:01:10.300
Inside, there are two memorable dining

00:01:10.300 --> 00:01:12.730
rooms. For Traditional dining, with fixed

00:01:12.730 --> 00:01:14.770
time and seating. And Anytime dining,

00:01:14.770 --> 00:01:16.810
where you can eat when and with whom you

00:01:16.810 --> 00:01:20.140
like. Specialty restaurants add savory

00:01:20.140 --> 00:01:23.110
temptations. Sabatini's provides a touch

00:01:23.110 --> 00:01:26.530
of romantic Italy. Or try the Bayou Café

00:01:26.530 --> 00:01:28.930
and Steakhouse for unforgettable Cajun

00:01:28.930 --> 00:01:33.250
and Creole cuisine. After dinner, there

00:01:33.250 --> 00:01:35.050
are plenty of venues to explore each

00:01:35.050 --> 00:01:37.900
evening. Check out the Casino, with

00:01:37.900 --> 00:01:42.670
blackjack, roulette, and slots. The exotic

00:01:42.670 --> 00:01:44.920
Explorers Lounge is home to an array of

00:01:44.920 --> 00:01:48.220
delightful performers. The spacious

00:01:48.220 --> 00:01:50.680
Universe Lounge is the place for lively

00:01:50.680 --> 00:01:53.590
entertainment. Enjoy the retro Rat Pack

00:01:53.590 --> 00:01:57.070
theme in Crooners Martini Bar, or step

00:01:57.070 --> 00:02:00.340
into the nautical-themed Wheelhouse Bar.

00:02:00.340 --> 00:02:03.170
Then, near the bow in the Princess

00:02:03.170 --> 00:02:05.840
Theater, enjoy the style and intricate

00:02:05.840 --> 00:02:07.970
choreography of stunning and original

00:02:07.970 --> 00:02:12.560
production shows. Coral Princess offers

00:02:12.560 --> 00:02:14.690
an array of inviting accommodations and

00:02:14.690 --> 00:02:18.770
deluxe amenities. Interior staterooms are

00:02:18.770 --> 00:02:21.110
well-appointed, comfortable, and offer an

00:02:21.110 --> 00:02:23.840
affordable option. An oceanview

00:02:23.840 --> 00:02:26.090
stateroom represents a great value, with

00:02:26.090 --> 00:02:29.030
your own picture window. To enjoy the

00:02:29.030 --> 00:02:31.190
fresh sea air and endless vistas, a

00:02:31.190 --> 00:02:33.460
balcony stateroom is the perfect choice.

00:02:33.460 --> 00:02:36.170
Pick a generous mini-suite, complete

00:02:36.170 --> 00:02:38.330
with separate sitting room, full bath, and

00:02:38.330 --> 00:02:42.170
ample balcony. Or indulge with an ultra-

00:02:42.170 --> 00:02:44.720
spacious full suite where amenities and

00:02:44.720 --> 00:02:49.160
service are unsurpassed. There's also a

00:02:49.160 --> 00:02:50.780
selection of rooms for our guests with

00:02:50.780 --> 00:02:52.940
disabilities, designed to provide maximum

00:02:52.940 --> 00:02:56.319
accessibility and comfort.

00:02:56.319 --> 00:02:59.499
Set a course for the spectacular Coral

00:02:59.499 --> 00:03:01.749
Princess, and you'll discover firsthand

00:03:01.749 --> 00:03:06.299
what it means to come back new.

